reviewText: Kelly is one of the most stunningly amazing women you will ever set your eyes on! The quality of the camera work shows how long ago this was shot but overlooking that, this is a great DVD. Yes, it is absolutely softcore, but then that is what many of us enjoy. If you are one of those collectors, then this is a must have as well as the Movies After Midnight 3 which also features Kelly in several vignettes. If you are looking for her hardcore work, look elsewhere, like her crappy website that has little of her on it.
